<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1237300.The_Shock_Doctrine"><img alt="The Shock Doctrine: The Rise of Disaster Capitalism" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1442590618l/1237300._SX98_.jpg" />
