<li class='cover' id='bookCover_389424'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/389424.Jinnah_of_Pakistan"><img alt="Jinnah of Pakistan" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1362367134l/389424._SY160_.jpg" />
